{"tid":2497383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台軍周五演練防衞「撐過一周」","createTime":"2021-04-20T13:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T13:02:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d988766ff28489a3ee583620f17bc34f87babccb","tid":2497383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210420/3TFVDIQXLZHY7OMMZ4YNBEXWA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210420%2F3TFVDIQXLZHY7OMMZ4YNBEXWA4%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=979e6193\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210420%2F3TFVDIQXLZHY7OMMZ4YNBEXWA4%2F&h=8533d869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210420/3TFVDIQXLZHY7OMMZ4YNBEXWA4/</a><br />\n<br />\n台軍周五演練防衞「撐過一周」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wNvkmgfAWUV-2zq3Iaf6vcNdXKI=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WC6AZGQMXFEGVKWEHH4MKEASIM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwNvkmgfAWUV-2zq3Iaf6vcNdXKI%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWC6AZGQMXFEGVKWEHH4MKEASIM.jpg&h=2b877bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台軍現有自走炮最「年輕」的都已服役逾20年；圖為去年漢光軍演。<br />\n<br />\n台軍將於本周五至下周五（23日至30日）舉行一年一度「漢光37號」兵棋推演，共8天7夜，創史上最長紀錄。這也是台灣國防部首度定下當解放軍犯台時，台軍在台澎防衞作戰可「撐過一周」的假想目標。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美擬售台反導彈自走炮  拜登上任首宗 抗解放軍登陸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n考慮疫情不邀美觀摩<br />\n<br />\n台灣防長邱國正昨日在立法院接受質詢時回應指，過往漢光兵棋推演的舉行日數一向是5天至7天不等，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於今年的「漢光37號」實兵演習則於7月12日至16日舉行，演習內容包括驗證西南空域戰術戰法、模擬軍方機場跑道遭炸毀，及戰機在屏東佳冬戰備跑道起降等。今年將動員8,000名後備軍人，令參演的軍人數目將達去年的8倍。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"}]}